stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> editing: 用户输入中

    editing --> previewing: AI 生成草稿预览
    previewing --> editing: 用户继续修改
    previewing --> confirmed: 用户确认写入

    confirmed --> generating_payload: AI 生成 MCP payload
    generating_payload --> validating: 后端校验 payload

    validating --> generating_payload: 需要 AI 修正
    validating --> blocked: 安全或权限异常
    validating --> syncing: 校验通过

    syncing --> success: 飞书写入成功
    syncing --> sync_failed: 飞书写入失败

    sync_failed --> syncing: 管理员或系统重试

    success --> displayed: 用户端展示
    blocked --> displayed: 展示异常状态

    displayed --> [*]
